title.rendered: Assess Steel Side Chair – end of line

content.rendered:
*This item is due to be discontinued. Price available whilst stocks last.*

The Assess Industrial Steel Side Chair is a commercial grade classroom-look chair perfect for industrial themes or those looking for a strong, care-free Side Chair.

Held in stock in a black steel frame with an oak veneered seat and backrest. 

Some self assembly may be required.
